snippet.title: Gor Lab - Launch Trailer | MS
snippet.description:
Available Now - 04/2022

https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/gor-lab/9nplfcqwqg41?activetab=pivot:overviewtab


The secret experiment at the Independent Research Gor Lab was a disaster when the incubation reactors exploded.

The Gor laboratory is manufacturing High-Tech Biotics and the recommendations to develop DNA-enhanced super-soldiers in the laboratory got more dangerous, with the results reading Negative, inducing a virus which could not be controlled by the scientists at the lab, and capable of bringing the apocalypse, the virus is beginning to affect the volunteers.

This virus and the infected humans must remain in the lab, and must not spread to the cities. You will hold the laboratory floors grounded and you must put the biosafety levels in check as you swing into action, fight till reinforcement is stationed, kill the virus. Gor laboratories must remain top-secret and classified.


Rated Mature: Blood, Violence
